1
00:01:38,980 --> 00:01:41,780
[Episode 8]

2
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:46,359
They're usually busy with business,
so they don't have time to dress up.

3
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:48,159
If we give them a proper makeover,

4
00:01:48,159 --> 00:01:49,799
the contrast will be huge.

5
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:53,239
Then, we'll put the "before" photos

6
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:56,519
and the "after" photos
side by side for comparison.

7
00:01:57,519 --> 00:02:00,000
The results will be clear.
The ad effect will be amazing.

8
00:02:00,879 --> 00:02:02,439
The slogan will be:

9
00:02:02,439 --> 00:02:06,959
Stylist Li works wonders,
Zhazhating women get new looks.

10
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:08,479
What do you think?
Help me remember it.

11
00:02:09,319 --> 00:02:11,119
Okay, that's a good one.

12
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:16,559
What about you?
You sure you won't be a model?

13
00:02:17,759 --> 00:02:19,199
Why does it have to be me?

14
00:02:19,199 --> 00:02:22,200
- Fuzz or Hu would work too.
- Because you're handsome.

15
00:02:29,479 --> 00:02:32,880
Well, thank you. You have good taste.

16
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:38,919
Suit yourself. Anyway, I've already

17
00:02:38,919 --> 00:02:41,999
given them my word
that the photos will look great.

18
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:45,919
- By the way, who's the photographer?
- Canine.

19
00:02:46,599 --> 00:02:49,080
Canine? Can he handle it?

20
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:52,399
I'm sure he can.

21
00:02:55,439 --> 00:02:58,599
- I can't.
- You can't, or you're afraid you can't?

22
00:02:58,599 --> 00:03:01,360
- A bit of both.
- How do you know if you don't try?

23
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:03,000
You often spend time studying cameras.

24
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,120
I just take photos for fun.

25
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:07,360
Just some casual shots. Not professional.

26
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:09,280
Even your casual shots are amazing.

27
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:12,199
Look at this. The scenery...
The landscape photo is great.

28
00:03:12,199 --> 00:03:13,560
Because the scenery is nice.

29
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:16,360
- The portrait is good too.
- Because my sister is pretty.

30
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:20,080
Don't put yourself down like that.

31
00:03:22,159 --> 00:03:24,400
Professional work... It's not that easy.

32
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,039
The reference photos Qing Ye sent me

33
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:28,039
are all masterpieces
by commercial photographers.

34
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:30,800
I'm just an amateur.
Even if I try to imitate them,

35
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:31,879
I don't have the gear or equipment.

36
00:03:31,879 --> 00:03:33,439
Says who?

37
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:43,750
- Where did you get a DSLR?
- If I said I bought it, would you buy it?

38
00:03:43,750 --> 00:03:44,870
Wu, you're crazy!

39
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,639
I can't believe
you bought such an expensive camera.

40
00:03:47,639 --> 00:03:53,639
- That's not important. Give it a try.
- All right.

41
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:06,000
Qing Ye. I've found everything.

42
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:10,960
I've been thinking. To attract customers,
you need publicity and exposure.

43
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:14,360
But to keep them, you need skills and talent.

44
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:18,160
Think about it. Xuan Island
keeps doing the same few hairstyles.

45
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,240
There's no innovation.

46
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:21,639
Naturally, that won't bring in
new customers or more income.

47
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:25,800
If we can figure out these styles
and create a few trending looks,

48
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:29,040
we won't have to worry about
foot traffic or low prices.

49
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:31,639
I don't know how to do any of these styles.

50
00:04:31,639 --> 00:04:35,000
Then learn. Just follow the examples, okay?

51
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:37,279
Curly hair is just about curling it.

52
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:40,160
It'll be fine.
You can never have too many skills.

53
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:42,120
If you can't learn it, no loss.
If you do, it's a huge win.

54
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,240
I guess you're right.

55
00:04:44,839 --> 00:04:47,199
But... how do I learn? Who will teach me?

56
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,360
Learn from online videos.

57
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:52,840
- I'll study it with you.
- Okay.

58
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:58,199
[Zhazhating]

59
00:04:59,199 --> 00:05:02,639
Fang, give me a hair treatment tonight.

60
00:05:02,639 --> 00:05:04,959
It's been years
since I last had my photo taken.

61
00:05:04,959 --> 00:05:07,519
- No problem.
- I need to look my best.

62
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:11,240
- You should get something done too.
- My hair isn't right for a treatment.

63
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:13,360
Then get a perm instead.

64
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,720
I'll get something wild then.

65
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:17,600
- Will that even look good?
- Oh my god!

66
00:05:21,959 --> 00:05:25,960
- Liu Nian?
- Fang. Does it look good?

67
00:05:27,279 --> 00:05:29,879
Did you get hit by a firecracker?

68
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:33,360
It's way too frizzy!

69
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,480
Doesn't it look good?

70
00:05:47,959 --> 00:05:50,520
Let me see what kind of perm you want.

71
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:56,600
- You want this one?
- Yes, this is it.

72
00:05:56,600 --> 00:06:00,000
Well... The rollers you used
were way too big.

73
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:03,439
This style is called a wool curl.

74
00:06:03,439 --> 00:06:06,950
It's for guys with thin
and soft hair texture.

75
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:09,040
You need to use small rollers

76
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:11,000
with a professional cold perm solution.

77
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,079
The timing matters too.

78
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:17,960
The curls are fine,
but they just don't suit you.

79
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:23,830
- What should we do then, Auntie?
- Watch and learn.

80
00:06:24,830 --> 00:06:26,270
You're trimming it?

81
00:06:26,270 --> 00:06:28,279
I already cut the back.

82
00:06:29,279 --> 00:06:30,759
It's already burnt.

83
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:34,399
Just a trim. A trim will fix it.

84
00:06:35,399 --> 00:06:39,360
Auntie, do you know how to do those styles?

85
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:42,160
I might not be an expert,

86
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:44,279
but I've seen it done plenty of times.

87
00:06:44,279 --> 00:06:46,600
There are many types of curls.

88
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:49,750
Foil perms, firework perms,

89
00:06:49,750 --> 00:06:52,360
root perms, cushion perms, and texture perms.

90
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:57,870
They all look like curls to you,
but the rollers used for each style,

91
00:06:57,870 --> 00:07:00,310
the perm solution, and the timing...

92
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:01,519
You have to master all of these.

93
00:07:02,519 --> 00:07:06,800
It mainly depends on the hair quality.
Some types are suitable, while others are not.

94
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:10,199
You can't just perm it
however you want.

95
00:07:20,759 --> 00:07:23,639
'A wonder-worker,' Auntie!

96
00:07:23,639 --> 00:07:26,639
Your skills are amazing.
He looks like a different person.

97
00:07:27,639 --> 00:07:32,999
- Qing Ye, how about we try one more time?
- On whom?

98
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:42,720
I have things to do. You young people,
figure it out yourselves.

99
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:43,439
- Auntie!
- Fang!

100
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:46,199
- Don't forget to sweep the floor! Bye-bye!
- Auntie!

101
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:52,560
- Off to play mahjong again.
- She ran off so fast.

102
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:55,639
So, who should we try it on?

103
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:06,160
- How about me?
- You?

104
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,975
The rollers are all set.

105
00:08:16,839 --> 00:08:18,105
Qing Ye,

106
00:08:18,105 --> 00:08:20,305
are you sure about this?

107
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:22,920
Let's do it.

108
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:25,523
You're going back to school after summer break.

109
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,680
So, do a good job.

110
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,759
You only have one shot.

111
00:08:29,759 --> 00:08:33,360
I'm just worried I'll mess up your hair.

112
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,380
It's fine.

113
00:08:34,380 --> 00:08:35,492
It's just hair.

114
00:08:35,492 --> 00:08:37,360
It'll always grow back.

115
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:39,642
Then I'm applying the solution.

116
00:08:42,759 --> 00:08:44,197
Go for it.

117
00:08:44,197 --> 00:08:46,639
Ye.

118
00:08:46,639 --> 00:08:47,919
- Grandma.
- Grandma.

119
00:08:47,919 --> 00:08:50,605
I'll give you one more chance.

120
00:08:50,605 --> 00:08:52,693
How about it?

121
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:59,480
Ye. Tell me.

122
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:02,270
If my hair turns out well,

123
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:03,581
could you take a photo

124
00:09:03,581 --> 00:09:05,670
for me tomorrow?

125
00:09:05,670 --> 00:09:07,270
Of course!

126
00:09:07,270 --> 00:09:11,559
That way, I'll have a collection
of Zhazhating beauties from every age group.

127
00:09:11,559 --> 00:09:12,938
That's wonderful.

128
00:09:12,938 --> 00:09:14,494
After I pass away,

129
00:09:14,494 --> 00:09:17,240
this will be my funeral portrait.

130
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:20,000
Grandma! Knock on wood!

131
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,787
How can you talk about yourself like that?

132
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,840
I'm already at this age.

133
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,519
I've got one foot in the grave.

134
00:09:27,519 --> 00:09:30,200
I've long since come to terms
with life and death.

135
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:33,039
What? You don't want to take it for me?

136
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:35,200
I do. Of course I'll take it.

137
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:37,320
Not just that.
I'll also put you on our poster

138
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:40,720
to attract middle-aged and elderly customers.

139
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:42,160
Then should I

140
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:43,272
ask Liu Nian

141
00:09:43,272 --> 00:09:45,000
to dye my hair a bit darker?

142
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,759
That'd make me look younger.

143
00:09:46,759 --> 00:09:48,960
You look young right now.
No need to dye it, Grandma.

144
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:51,537
This is exactly the look I want.

145
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:11,440
Xiao Liu, your skills are truly impressive.

146
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:13,120
Thanks to Fang's guidance.

147
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,640
And Qing Ye taught me well.

148
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:15,755
Not at all.

149
00:10:15,755 --> 00:10:18,030
Grandma, it looks really beautiful.

150
00:10:18,030 --> 00:10:20,279
You should have permed it sooner.

151
00:10:20,279 --> 00:10:23,879
Do I look ten years younger now?

152
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:26,800
I'd say you'd found the fountain of youth.

153
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:31,200
Liu Nian, hurry. Take out Ye's rollers too,
and let's see how hers turns out.

154
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:34,122
Okay. Here we go.

155
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:14,360
Qing Ye, open your eyes!

156
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:17,074
Open your eyes and take a look.

157
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:28,320
We did it!

158
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,600
It's a success, right?

159
00:11:29,600 --> 00:11:31,080
- Grandma, do I look good?
- Definitely a success.

160
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:33,440
You look great.

161
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:37,279
Liu Nian, you're a real perm genius!

162
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:40,840
My grandma used to say that too,
but I never believed her.

163
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,519
I still need more practice, though.

164
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:45,399
It's mainly because your hair quality is good
and you have a lot of hair.

165
00:11:45,399 --> 00:11:46,812
But, Qing Ye,

166
00:11:46,812 --> 00:11:49,360
this hairstyle really suits you.

167
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:51,720
I should go show my auntie right now.

168
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:54,900
- Let her see the results.
- Okay.

169
00:11:54,900 --> 00:11:56,233
[Xuan Island Barbershop]

170
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:27,130
How do I look?

171
00:12:27,920 --> 00:12:31,512
The new hairstyle is nice.

172
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:37,559
You look like... What's her name
from that movie? The red-haired princess.

173
00:12:37,559 --> 00:12:40,098
- Merida?
- Right.

174
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:44,159
But my hair is black.

175
00:12:45,559 --> 00:12:48,353
Black hair looks
better than red hair.

176
00:12:49,339 --> 00:12:51,630
Black hair is beautiful.

177
00:13:04,039 --> 00:13:05,225
It looks good, right?

178
00:13:05,225 --> 00:13:06,600
Grandma.

179
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:08,080
Wu.

180
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,320
- Come look.
- You're back.

181
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:11,919
Does my new hair look good?

182
00:13:11,919 --> 00:13:14,480
It looks good. Really.

183
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:18,320
Auntie, look at my new hairstyle.

184
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,600
- It's so pretty.
- Really beautiful.

185
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:24,000
- It's so cute!
- It's so stylish. It looks great.

186
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:27,519
So this is the style
you and Liu Nian came up with?

187
00:13:27,519 --> 00:13:30,840
Not bad, you two. You're quite impressive.

188
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:32,720
To pull off such a difficult style.

189
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:33,947
Alright, alright.

190
00:13:33,947 --> 00:13:36,799
Someone just said I look like Merida.

191
00:13:36,799 --> 00:13:38,061
Meri-what?

192
00:13:38,061 --> 00:13:39,639
Very charming!

193
00:13:39,639 --> 00:13:43,010
Who's so sweet?

194
00:13:45,700 --> 00:13:48,020
[Open]

195
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:53,400
Dyeing: 188 yuan.

196
00:13:53,400 --> 00:13:55,320
Perming: 288 yuan.

197
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:59,759
Dye &amp; Perm Package: 368 yuan.

198
00:13:59,759 --> 00:14:01,386
Is the price a bit too high?

199
00:14:01,386 --> 00:14:02,759
No one will come then.

200
00:14:02,759 --> 00:14:05,400
I've checked the prices
of several shops in the county.

201
00:14:05,400 --> 00:14:06,480
Their perming quality

202
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:09,720
is about the same as ours,
but they charge even more.

203
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:13,280
I think as long as it's within their budget,

204
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:16,910
customers are willing to pay
for high-quality service.

205
00:14:16,910 --> 00:14:18,270
Besides, Auntie,

206
00:14:18,270 --> 00:14:20,000
if you set the price higher now,

207
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:22,062
we'll have room to lower it later.

208
00:14:22,062 --> 00:14:23,915
Is that so?

209
00:14:24,761 --> 00:14:25,880
Alright then.

210
00:14:25,880 --> 00:14:28,180
I'll listen to you for now.

211
00:14:29,279 --> 00:14:32,279
"Summer sale, member benefits."

212
00:14:32,279 --> 00:14:34,639
We're also starting membership services?

213
00:14:34,639 --> 00:14:36,519
Profit, we need profit!

214
00:14:36,519 --> 00:14:39,960
Can't just leave things to fate
every day when we open for business.

215
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:44,440
- So they have to prepay? 288 for 10% off.
- Exactly.

216
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:46,150
488 for 20% off.

217
00:14:46,150 --> 00:14:47,840
688 for 30% off.

218
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:50,120
In the past, a haircut cost 15 yuan.

219
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:53,120
If we suddenly raise it to 20,

220
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:54,600
customers will think it's too much

221
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:56,279
- and stop coming.
- Exactly.

222
00:14:56,279 --> 00:14:57,978
That's why we need to get these plans,

223
00:14:57,978 --> 00:15:00,919
posters, and
flyers out there.

224
00:15:00,919 --> 00:15:03,000
Moreover, we also need word of mouth.

225
00:15:03,000 --> 00:15:05,790
We have to get new and old customers
to sign up.

226
00:15:05,790 --> 00:15:07,640
You have to let them know
that after signing up,

227
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:09,577
haircuts will only cost about ten yuan.

228
00:15:09,577 --> 00:15:11,270
Plus these discounts,

229
00:15:11,270 --> 00:15:13,200
a haircut will actually
only cost a few yuan.

230
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,720
That's way too cheap.

231
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:17,743
We want them to feel like
they're getting a huge bargain.

232
00:15:17,743 --> 00:15:19,600
Then our promotional goal will be achieved.

233
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:22,150
But we can't afford to lose money.

234
00:15:22,150 --> 00:15:23,480
Auntie, don't worry.

235
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:25,630
We'll definitely make a profit.

236
00:15:25,630 --> 00:15:27,358
If they sign up for a card... look,

237
00:15:27,358 --> 00:15:29,000
288, 488, or 688 yuan.

238
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:31,870
Once they pay that much upfront,
they'll definitely keep coming back, right?

239
00:15:31,870 --> 00:15:34,630
That means we've both secured our customers

240
00:15:34,630 --> 00:15:36,200
and gained cash flow.

241
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:39,840
We're getting repeat customers
and making money at the same time.

242
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:42,000
- I guess you're right.
- Fang!

243
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:44,200
You're here!

244
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:47,080
I don't just want a deep conditioning,
I want a perm too.

245
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,720
- Sure thing!
- I want a perm as well.

246
00:15:48,720 --> 00:15:50,480
No problem at all. Liu Nian, you're up!

247
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:51,639
One for each of you.

248
00:15:51,639 --> 00:15:54,159
- Okay, the seats are yours.
- You sit here.

249
00:15:54,159 --> 00:15:58,840
Auntie, here's the word-of-mouth marketing.

250
00:15:58,840 --> 00:16:01,640
Get them to sign up for cards.

251
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:03,815
Okay.

252
00:16:06,120 --> 00:16:10,960
We absolutely cannot treat Xuan Island
like just a small shop.

253
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:13,480
We have to think big.

254
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:16,200
To attract customers,
we need everyone nearby to know about us.

255
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:18,159
Word needs to spread like wildfire.

256
00:16:18,159 --> 00:16:19,960
And what is our main draw?

257
00:16:19,960 --> 00:16:21,292
It's our technique.

258
00:16:21,292 --> 00:16:22,600
That's our golden reputation.

259
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:24,559
So I'm counting on everyone

260
00:16:24,559 --> 00:16:26,559
to help spread the word.

261
00:16:26,559 --> 00:16:28,274
We've got a real buzz going.

262
00:16:28,274 --> 00:16:29,480
But Qing Ye...

263
00:16:29,480 --> 00:16:31,080
We've planned so much.

264
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:33,960
- But what if no one shows up?
- Yeah.

265
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,759
That's why we must take action.

266
00:16:35,759 --> 00:16:38,200
We need to strike while the iron is hot
and keep the momentum going.

267
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:40,120
If there are problems, we solve them.

268
00:16:40,120 --> 00:16:44,200
But we can't count ourselves out
before we've even started.

269
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:45,886
Right.

270
00:16:46,680 --> 00:16:49,022
Ye, you really have great ideas.

271
00:16:49,022 --> 00:16:50,600
You have a real business mind.

272
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:53,039
We've been in business for half our lives,

273
00:16:53,039 --> 00:16:55,320
yet we're no match for a young girl
at planning.

274
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:57,320
- Exactly.
- True.

275
00:16:57,320 --> 00:17:00,559
Since Ye is such a good planner, I trust you.

276
00:17:00,559 --> 00:17:01,679
- You trust me?
- I do!

277
00:17:01,679 --> 00:17:03,120
- Trust me?
- Yes, we trust you!

278
00:17:03,120 --> 00:17:05,474
Qing Ye, you know so much.

279
00:17:05,474 --> 00:17:08,440
- Where did you learn all of this?
- Exactly.

280
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:12,319
I heard my dad talk about
the ins and outs of his business.

281
00:17:12,319 --> 00:17:14,600
I didn't think it would come in handy today.

282
00:17:14,600 --> 00:17:16,839
I've applied it all to Xuan Island.

283
00:17:16,839 --> 00:17:20,359
True. My brother-in-law
is a big-time businessman.

284
00:17:20,359 --> 00:17:21,440
What's the saying?

285
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:24,000
"Dragons beget dragons,
and phoenixes beget phoenixes.

286
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:27,836
A rat's son knows how to dig holes."

287
00:17:27,836 --> 00:17:29,160
You two are so annoying.

288
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:31,880
Ye just learned by example.

289
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:34,839
- So, Qing Ye, what else do we need to prepare?
- Right.

290
00:17:34,839 --> 00:17:37,880
Everything is ready.
We just need the promotional materials.

291
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:40,359
So tomorrow, everyone must

292
00:17:40,359 --> 00:17:41,799
be in top form.

293
00:17:41,799 --> 00:17:43,000
Top form.

294
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:44,759
- Top form...
- Top form...

295
00:17:44,759 --> 00:17:47,687
- Top form!
- Top form!

296
00:17:47,687 --> 00:17:49,675
Great!

297
00:17:49,675 --> 00:17:52,839
- Your hair looks really good.
- I'm almost done, right?

298
00:17:52,839 --> 00:17:53,880
I wonder how mine looks.

299
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:55,359
- I'm sure yours looks great too.
- Really?

300
00:17:55,359 --> 00:17:56,960
- Trust me.
- It's permed. The color is great.

301
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:58,160
- No, no.
- Look at this.

302
00:17:58,160 --> 00:18:02,070
- I need a good hairstyle to be in top form.
- Beautiful.

303
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:08,040
I'll count down from three,

304
00:18:08,040 --> 00:18:10,440
and you just walk forward naturally.
We'll take candid shots.

305
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:14,793
- Okay, okay.
- Okay, here we go. Three, two, one, go!

306
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:18,966
Wait! Stop! You're all walking wrong.

307
00:18:18,966 --> 00:18:20,079
- We are?
- Really?

308
00:18:20,079 --> 00:18:21,279
- We are.
- Okay.

309
00:18:21,279 --> 00:18:23,640
- Let's coordinate.
- Be more in sync.

310
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:25,279
Left foot first, right? Okay.

311
00:18:25,279 --> 00:18:26,359
Right. Yes. Left.

312
00:18:26,359 --> 00:18:30,078
Okay, here we go. Three, two, one, go!

313
00:18:30,078 --> 00:18:32,000
Looking good. Be more natural.

314
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:33,240
Show off your aura.

315
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:37,000
Looking good, looking good.
Take slightly bigger steps.

316
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:38,240
Mom?

317
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,480
Son!

318
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:42,400
Mom! What happened to you?

319
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:44,680
Don't call me Mom. Call me Sis.

320
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:47,759
Well... Mom-Sis.

321
00:18:47,759 --> 00:18:49,519
Please call me Xi Xi.

322
00:18:49,519 --> 00:18:52,480
You ungrateful brat!
I changed my hairstyle last night,

323
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:54,799
and you didn't even notice.

324
00:18:54,799 --> 00:18:56,124
Do I look good today?

325
00:18:56,124 --> 00:18:57,839
- Look at these curls.
- Don't mess it up.

326
00:18:57,839 --> 00:18:59,799
Ladies! We're losing the light!

327
00:18:59,799 --> 00:19:02,480
- Don't move!
- Hurry up.

328
00:19:02,480 --> 00:19:04,119
Kim Hee Seon!

329
00:19:04,119 --> 00:19:06,791
Lin Chi-ling!

330
00:19:07,559 --> 00:19:09,026
Lydia Sum!

331
00:19:09,026 --> 00:19:10,440
You're so annoying.

332
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:13,599
- Get lost!
- Go cook dinner. Go on.

333
00:19:13,599 --> 00:19:15,039
We're losing the light!

334
00:19:15,039 --> 00:19:16,759
- Get in position.
- Come on.

335
00:19:16,759 --> 00:19:20,880
- Let's walk properly.
- Ready? Three, two, one, go!

336
00:19:20,880 --> 00:19:22,759
Beautiful! Looking good!

337
00:19:22,759 --> 00:19:25,480
Aura! Show your aura! "I'm the prettiest!"

338
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:27,680
"I'm the most beautiful!" Touch your hair.

339
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:30,440
Touch your curls. Those curls look amazing.

340
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:32,400
They do look much younger.

341
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:34,640
My mom wants me to call her "Sis".

342
00:19:34,640 --> 00:19:37,160
Then my dad would have to call me...

343
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:39,638
"Little Brother"?

344
00:19:40,498 --> 00:19:42,547
Nuts.

345
00:19:43,319 --> 00:19:45,360
Grandma, sip the coffee. I'm shooting now.

346
00:19:45,360 --> 00:19:48,772
Don't look at us. Just keep chatting.

347
00:20:16,880 --> 00:20:19,200
- Look at the camera.
- Look at you.

348
00:20:19,200 --> 00:20:22,279
Three, two, one.

349
00:20:22,279 --> 00:20:24,559
- One more.
- Let me change my pose.

350
00:20:24,559 --> 00:20:27,279
- Come on.
- Relax a bit, relax.

351
00:20:27,279 --> 00:20:30,220
Say cheese!

352
00:20:30,220 --> 00:20:32,060
[Xuan Island Barbershop]

353
00:20:34,359 --> 00:20:36,599
It looks so good.

354
00:20:36,599 --> 00:20:38,200
This one is so cool.

355
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:40,748
Mr. Liu, have you received the RAM stick?

356
00:20:40,748 --> 00:20:42,985
Yes, I did.

357
00:20:42,985 --> 00:20:44,960
Okay. Thanks for the camera.

358
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:46,559
I'll return it to you tonight.

359
00:20:46,559 --> 00:20:49,492
Okay, no problem.

360
00:20:52,799 --> 00:20:55,185
Oh my god!

361
00:20:56,799 --> 00:20:58,319
- This is great!
- How about this?

362
00:20:58,319 --> 00:20:59,559
Let's make it tomorrow.

363
00:20:59,559 --> 00:21:01,800
I'll bring it over first thing
in the morning. Is that okay?

364
00:21:01,800 --> 00:21:02,829
No problem.

365
00:21:02,829 --> 00:21:04,400
Thanks a lot.

366
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,960
Bye.

367
00:21:05,960 --> 00:21:08,559
Ladies! Watermelon is here!

368
00:21:08,559 --> 00:21:10,079
Come and have some watermelon.

369
00:21:10,079 --> 00:21:13,039
- Son, you sliced these really well. Come on.
- That's so thoughtful.

370
00:21:13,039 --> 00:21:14,640
- Eat up.
- Here, one piece each.

371
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:18,001
- Grandma, try some.
- Ye, here.

372
00:21:30,839 --> 00:21:32,960
- For me?
- Cool yourself down.

373
00:21:32,960 --> 00:21:34,715
Thanks.

374
00:21:34,715 --> 00:21:36,920
Canine's photos are really good.

375
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:39,200
Like magazine shots. How did you know?

376
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:42,380
I've known him for many years.
Of course I'd know.

377
00:21:43,119 --> 00:21:46,319
Everyone is much more proactive
about this than I imagined.

378
00:21:46,319 --> 00:21:49,220
Especially Auntie. She's all in.

379
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:53,888
It's been a long time
since Zhazhating has been this lively.

380
00:21:55,839 --> 00:21:57,440
How should I put it?

381
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:59,839
Whether Xuan Island's business picks up or not,

382
00:21:59,839 --> 00:22:03,710
at least everyone
had a great time together today.

383
00:22:06,720 --> 00:22:09,354
- Cheers with the melon.
- Melon.

384
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:13,320
Look over here.

385
00:22:13,320 --> 00:22:15,663
One more.

386
00:22:17,279 --> 00:22:20,226
Change your pose, one more.

387
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:31,880
I told you that you have talent.

388
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:34,319
These are great.

389
00:22:34,319 --> 00:22:36,186
Xing Wu, look at this one.

390
00:22:36,186 --> 00:22:38,219
It's so good.

391
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:43,080
Because it's natural
with a sense of story and atmosphere.

392
00:22:43,080 --> 00:22:45,641
The photographer is great too.

393
00:22:45,641 --> 00:22:49,000
I suggest we include
this photo in the poster.

394
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:50,877
It'll definitely attract customers.

395
00:22:53,200 --> 00:22:55,200
No problem.

396
00:22:57,480 --> 00:22:59,559
No rush to return the camera, right?

397
00:22:59,559 --> 00:23:01,880
Then I'll take a few more.

398
00:23:01,880 --> 00:23:05,146
No rush. Take as many as you want.

399
00:23:07,119 --> 00:23:09,600
Come on, everyone, look at me again.
I'll take some more.

400
00:23:09,600 --> 00:23:11,200
A few more shots.

401
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:13,119
Three, two, one.

402
00:23:13,119 --> 00:23:16,760
- Cheese!
- Cheese!

403
00:23:37,055 --> 00:23:38,400
[1,700 yuan transferred]

404
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:40,720
- Liu Nian, I've transferred your pay.
- Wu.

405
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:43,279
- Remember to check it.
- Wu, you sent 500 yuan extra.

406
00:23:43,279 --> 00:23:45,480
Just a small token.
The shop has been busy lately,

407
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:47,799
and you've been studying techniques.
You've worked hard.

408
00:23:47,799 --> 00:23:49,279
But you work hard for your money too.

409
00:23:49,279 --> 00:23:50,880
I'm an assistant at the shop.

410
00:23:50,880 --> 00:23:52,759
This is all part of my job.

411
00:23:52,759 --> 00:23:55,040
Besides, I'm indebted to you and Fang.

412
00:23:55,040 --> 00:23:57,632
That's different. Just keep it.

413
00:23:58,667 --> 00:23:59,830
Wu.

414
00:23:59,830 --> 00:24:03,359
How about this?
I'll treat everyone to a meal with this 500.

415
00:24:03,359 --> 00:24:04,759
I can't let you pay for that.

416
00:24:04,759 --> 00:24:06,018
When we're done here,

417
00:24:06,018 --> 00:24:07,359
I'll get everyone together.

418
00:24:07,359 --> 00:24:08,422
It's my treat.

419
00:24:08,422 --> 00:24:10,405
Okay.

420
00:24:19,279 --> 00:24:21,994
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

421
00:24:24,599 --> 00:24:27,559
On behalf of Xuan Island, thank you.

422
00:24:27,559 --> 00:24:29,160
Thank me?

423
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:32,352
I should thank you too,
for choosing to believe in me.

424
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:36,520
Qing Ye,

425
00:24:36,520 --> 00:24:39,480
if it weren't for you,
I wouldn't have known I could be this good.

426
00:24:39,480 --> 00:24:41,119
Thank you for your encouragement.

427
00:24:41,119 --> 00:24:42,160
Let me toast
to you.

428
00:24:42,160 --> 00:24:44,440
Don't mention it. You're amazing.

429
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:45,680
Cousin,

430
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:48,079
if you ever need anything,
just let me know.

431
00:24:48,079 --> 00:24:51,960
In Zhazhating, Wu has my back,
and I have yours.

432
00:24:51,960 --> 00:24:53,920
Okay. Let me apologize first.

433
00:24:53,920 --> 00:24:56,440
I wasn't very nice to you before.

434
00:24:56,440 --> 00:25:00,119
It's fine. I wouldn't take it seriously
with two guys drinking juice.

435
00:25:00,119 --> 00:25:01,665
We all know how boring

436
00:25:01,665 --> 00:25:04,200
our summer vacation was before you came.

437
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:05,640
It's much more fun with you here.

438
00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:07,906
- Here's to you.
- Okay.

439
00:25:09,239 --> 00:25:11,959
Because of you, Wu got me a DSLR.

440
00:25:11,959 --> 00:25:13,560
Now I know
how interesting portrait photography is.

441
00:25:14,159 --> 00:25:17,373
When my sister comes back from Hainan...

442
00:25:18,671 --> 00:25:20,853
Drink up.

443
00:25:26,120 --> 00:25:27,600
You're all thanking me,

444
00:25:28,199 --> 00:25:30,840
but actually, when I first arrived,

445
00:25:30,840 --> 00:25:32,453
I really hated this place.

446
00:25:32,453 --> 00:25:34,933
I especially hated you.

447
00:25:35,920 --> 00:25:38,680
But now that I think about it,

448
00:25:38,680 --> 00:25:41,520
if it weren't for you, I'd probably be

449
00:25:41,520 --> 00:25:45,113
on some street in Beijing,
wandering around right now.

450
00:25:46,680 --> 00:25:50,093
So, thank you, Xing Wu.

451
00:25:50,093 --> 00:25:52,006
You're a good person.

452
00:25:55,040 --> 00:25:57,399
You're calling me a "good person" now?

453
00:25:57,399 --> 00:25:59,633
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

454
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:03,840
Lastly, I'd like to toast everyone.

455
00:26:03,840 --> 00:26:05,960
Let's celebrate Xuan Island's

456
00:26:05,960 --> 00:26:08,639
successful first step. Cheers!

457
00:26:08,639 --> 00:26:12,673
- Okay. Cheers!
- Cheers!

458
00:26:16,880 --> 00:26:18,493
- Let's eat.
- Eat up.

459
00:26:18,493 --> 00:26:20,780
Have some shrimp.

460
00:26:22,360 --> 00:26:23,826
Hello?

461
00:26:25,959 --> 00:26:28,606
Okay. I'll be right there.

462
00:26:30,159 --> 00:26:32,399
- Where are you going?
- Auntie Zhou's Wi-Fi is down.

463
00:26:32,399 --> 00:26:34,919
- I have to go check it out.
- Can't it wait until tomorrow?

464
00:26:34,919 --> 00:26:37,080
Her kid has an online class. It's urgent.

465
00:26:37,080 --> 00:26:39,486
You guys eat. I'll be right back.

466
00:26:40,133 --> 00:26:41,760
- Bye.
- Bye.

467
00:26:41,760 --> 00:26:44,013
- I'll be back soon!
- Okay.

468
00:26:44,840 --> 00:26:47,440
Qing Ye, eat up. This is standard for Wu.

469
00:26:47,440 --> 00:26:49,840
He often leaves in the middle
of a meal to go work.

470
00:26:49,840 --> 00:26:51,200
- Let's eat.
- Come on, eat up.

471
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:52,560
- Don't mind him. Eat.
- Eat.

472
00:26:52,560 --> 00:26:54,131
Come on.

473
00:26:54,131 --> 00:26:55,360
Let's have another drink.

474
00:26:55,360 --> 00:26:56,800
- Come on.
- Cheers!

475
00:26:56,800 --> 00:26:59,320
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

476
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:22,900
Doesn't she get tired?

477
00:27:23,520 --> 00:27:26,113
Her head might be fuzzy,

478
00:27:26,113 --> 00:27:28,199
but her legs are definitely awake.

479
00:27:28,199 --> 00:27:32,033
A grand jeté! Two grand jetés!

480
00:27:45,280 --> 00:27:47,266
What's going on?

481
00:27:48,466 --> 00:27:50,840
I was only gone for a little while.
You guys drank so much?

482
00:27:50,840 --> 00:27:52,159
Where are the others?

483
00:27:52,159 --> 00:27:54,200
I don't know.

484
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:56,260
Where's Qing Ye?

485
00:27:57,199 --> 00:27:58,800
Over there.

486
00:27:58,800 --> 00:28:01,379
The swan of the beach!

487
00:28:01,379 --> 00:28:03,260
Great dancing!

488
00:28:04,960 --> 00:28:07,040
This way. Right! Over here!

489
00:28:07,040 --> 00:28:08,740
And then...

490
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:13,640
Curtain call! Curtain call.

491
00:28:13,640 --> 00:28:15,486
What's gotten into her?

492
00:28:16,548 --> 00:28:18,000
Wu.

493
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:20,800
I... I can even do a backflip!

494
00:28:20,800 --> 00:28:22,240
Why didn't you two stop her?

495
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:24,139
We couldn't.

496
00:28:24,139 --> 00:28:25,800
There was no stopping her.

497
00:28:25,800 --> 00:28:27,649
You should've kept an eye on her!

498
00:28:27,649 --> 00:28:29,239
Let's go.

499
00:28:29,239 --> 00:28:31,740
We tried our best!

500
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,559
Alright. Let's call it a day.

501
00:28:35,559 --> 00:28:37,080
Take those two back. They've fallen asleep.

502
00:28:37,080 --> 00:28:38,680
Wait. She did two rounds before this.

503
00:28:38,680 --> 00:28:40,280
- Want to see?
- Get lost.

504
00:28:40,280 --> 00:28:42,420
- Really.
- Get lost.

505
00:28:47,959 --> 00:28:50,400
- Take them back home.
- Okay.

506
00:28:50,400 --> 00:28:53,560
I can also... backflip.

507
00:28:53,560 --> 00:28:57,240
Spin around... And then...

508
00:28:58,159 --> 00:29:02,300
Look, I can spin like this. Like this.

509
00:29:06,040 --> 00:29:08,053
What other acts?

510
00:29:09,360 --> 00:29:11,494
Xing Wu, dear.

511
00:29:14,520 --> 00:29:17,120
Dear!

512
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:24,413
Hurry... Come down now.

513
00:29:25,800 --> 00:29:27,926
Come down now.

514
00:29:29,120 --> 00:29:31,439
Hurry and come down, please.

515
00:29:31,439 --> 00:29:33,933
Okay, I'm coming down.

516
00:29:36,120 --> 00:29:37,453
This way.

517
00:29:39,080 --> 00:29:41,773
Slowly.

518
00:29:43,640 --> 00:29:44,979
Xing Wu, dear.

519
00:29:44,979 --> 00:29:47,046
Did I dance well just now?

520
00:29:47,046 --> 00:29:49,160
Yes, it was beautiful.

521
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:52,560
Then, are we... considered family now?

522
00:29:52,560 --> 00:29:54,480
- Of course.
- Then...

523
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:57,800
Shouldn't family members
tell each other the truth?

524
00:29:57,800 --> 00:29:59,226
Yes.

525
00:29:59,226 --> 00:30:01,600
My truth is...

526
00:30:01,600 --> 00:30:05,840
I want Xuan Island
to make lots and lots of money.

527
00:30:05,840 --> 00:30:08,440
After that...

528
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:11,600
I'll... support you.

529
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:13,960
- I mean it! I'll buy you...
- All right.

530
00:30:13,960 --> 00:30:15,439
A big mansion!

531
00:30:15,439 --> 00:30:17,640
A huge, huge bed!

532
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:20,439
- Slow down.
- I'm serious!

533
00:30:20,439 --> 00:30:22,960
Trust me. I'm a woman of my word!

534
00:30:22,960 --> 00:30:25,906
Okay. But actually, I don't mind.

535
00:30:26,552 --> 00:30:28,526
No.

536
00:30:29,215 --> 00:30:31,933
You can't not mind.

537
00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:34,446
Why?

538
00:30:34,446 --> 00:30:38,200
Because you work so hard.

539
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:39,773
What?

540
00:30:40,733 --> 00:30:42,940
I said...

541
00:30:47,919 --> 00:30:51,100
Because you work so hard.

542
00:30:51,880 --> 00:30:54,313
It pains me.

543
00:31:14,560 --> 00:31:16,580
It pains you?

544
00:31:19,280 --> 00:31:23,760
If Xuan Island makes lots and lots of money,

545
00:31:24,840 --> 00:31:26,919
then maybe

546
00:31:26,919 --> 00:31:31,086
you won't have to work so hard.

547
00:31:45,320 --> 00:31:49,533
I'll perform another show for you. Just wait.

548
00:31:55,200 --> 00:31:59,546
Have you seen the Monkey King's birth
from a stone? Like this!

549
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:14,840
- We're rich.
- What is that?

550
00:32:14,840 --> 00:32:16,926
We're rich!

551
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:20,880
Xing Wu! We've struck it rich!

552
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:24,240
Jade! It's Imperial Green!

553
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:27,233
We're rich, Xing Wu!

554
00:32:27,233 --> 00:32:29,400
- Look!
- Oh, boy.

555
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:31,880
- Seriously. It's Imperial Green.
- Right?

556
00:32:31,880 --> 00:32:33,611
Let's sell it.

557
00:32:33,611 --> 00:32:38,520
Then, we can live in a big villa.

558
00:32:38,520 --> 00:32:43,280
I... I'm going to buy you a house now.
Just wait.

559
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:46,520
I'm going to buy you a villa!

560
00:32:46,520 --> 00:32:48,600
Wait, how? Take a boat?

561
00:32:48,600 --> 00:32:51,239
That's right. We have to go out to sea.

562
00:32:51,239 --> 00:32:53,080
Buy it on the other side.

563
00:32:53,080 --> 00:32:55,139
Let's go. Captain.

564
00:32:55,139 --> 00:32:56,600
Hurry. Set sail.

565
00:32:56,600 --> 00:32:59,920
- Captain?
- We have to set off.

566
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:03,300
Okay. The Captain is setting sail.

567
00:33:03,300 --> 00:33:05,800
Let's go! Let's set off!

568
00:33:10,199 --> 00:33:13,239
Jack!

569
00:33:14,239 --> 00:33:17,753
You jump, I jump.

570
00:33:20,159 --> 00:33:22,760
Okay, Rose.

571
00:33:25,679 --> 00:33:27,366
Jack.

572
00:33:28,127 --> 00:33:30,269
Jack!

573
00:33:30,269 --> 00:33:32,215
- Rose.
- Jack.

574
00:33:32,215 --> 00:33:34,200
- Rose!
- Jack!

575
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:36,260
- Rose!
- Let's go!

576
00:33:51,399 --> 00:33:54,098
Xing Wu, your

577
00:33:54,098 --> 00:33:56,280
family...

578
00:33:56,280 --> 00:34:00,320
I really like your family.

579
00:34:00,320 --> 00:34:02,680
It's really nice.

580
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:05,360
The house is nice too.

581
00:34:05,360 --> 00:34:07,840
But there's no...

582
00:34:07,840 --> 00:34:11,559
There's no closet.

583
00:34:11,559 --> 00:34:15,160
No closet to put clothes in.

584
00:34:16,160 --> 00:34:19,320
And your house is so hot.

585
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:22,760
There are so many mosquitoes too.

586
00:34:22,760 --> 00:34:25,186
It's so hot.

587
00:34:26,519 --> 00:34:28,519
- It's hot.
- There's no closet.

588
00:34:28,519 --> 00:34:31,080
Then I'll turn on the AC.

589
00:34:31,080 --> 00:34:33,800
No closet for clothes.

590
00:34:33,800 --> 00:34:38,519
A closet... I'll figure something out.

591
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:42,519
- I want... a closet...
- What else?

592
00:34:42,519 --> 00:34:45,426
for lots of clothes.

593
00:35:32,820 --> 00:35:34,460
[Relieve hangover and protect liver.
Take two tablets once.]

594
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:37,300
[Drink more warm water.]

595
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:07,240
What are you doing so early?

596
00:36:07,240 --> 00:36:10,080
Early? Look at what time it is.

597
00:36:10,080 --> 00:36:12,846
- It's already afternoon, Qing Ye.
- One o'clock.

598
00:36:12,846 --> 00:36:14,200
You didn't wake me up?

599
00:36:14,200 --> 00:36:16,920
I did. But you wouldn't wake up.

600
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:18,760
You drank too much last night?

601
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:21,300
I passed out as soon as
my head hit the pillow.

602
00:36:23,160 --> 00:36:25,053
What are you laughing at?

603
00:36:25,834 --> 00:36:27,766
Don't you remember?

604
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:35,280
Remember what?

605
00:36:35,280 --> 00:36:38,859
Actually, it's fine.
It's nothing. Better you don't remember.

606
00:36:40,640 --> 00:36:43,599
- What is it?
- It's so hot.

607
00:36:43,599 --> 00:36:45,519
Let's go buy some popsicles.

608
00:36:45,519 --> 00:36:47,079
Okay. What do you want, Qing Ye?

609
00:36:47,079 --> 00:36:50,206
- I'm not eating.
- I'll just pick something for you then.

610
00:36:56,399 --> 00:36:59,688
Is there something you're not telling me?

611
00:37:00,440 --> 00:37:01,559
Yes.

612
00:37:01,559 --> 00:37:04,960
- What is it?
- You want to know?

613
00:37:06,280 --> 00:37:08,519
What happened? What did I do later on?

614
00:37:08,519 --> 00:37:10,965
Do you really want to know?

615
00:37:10,965 --> 00:37:13,376
Just tell me already!

616
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:19,173
Well, last night...

617
00:37:43,720 --> 00:37:45,806
<i>Want to throw up?</i>

618
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:53,365
<i>I realized...</i>

619
00:37:53,365 --> 00:37:55,793
<i>that you...</i>

620
00:37:56,640 --> 00:37:58,880
<i>have a great quality.</i>

621
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:04,033
<i>What quality?</i>

622
00:38:04,033 --> 00:38:06,280
<i>Do you want to know?</i>

623
00:38:13,720 --> 00:38:17,000
<i>You have such a perky butt!</i>

624
00:38:24,039 --> 00:38:26,400
<i>It's so perky.</i>

625
00:38:39,200 --> 00:38:43,126
I said you have... a perky butt?

626
00:38:43,880 --> 00:38:45,640
You're too kind.

627
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:49,039
I'm crazy! I've really gone crazy. Help me!

628
00:38:49,039 --> 00:38:51,980
What's wrong, Ye?

629
00:38:54,320 --> 00:38:57,919
- What's wrong with her?
- Probably did something shameful.

630
00:38:57,919 --> 00:39:00,040
Don't talk nonsense. She's a good girl.

631
00:39:00,040 --> 00:39:03,520
How could she have done anything shameful?

632
00:39:03,520 --> 00:39:06,526
Well, you don't know. She has many sides

633
00:39:06,526 --> 00:39:10,126
that people don't know about.
I just found out myself.

634
00:39:13,215 --> 00:39:15,280
The white fungus soup I made is almost ready.

635
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:16,760
Bring her a bowl later.

636
00:39:16,760 --> 00:39:18,720
No. You go.

637
00:39:18,720 --> 00:39:20,418
What's wrong?

638
00:39:20,418 --> 00:39:23,876
I bet she's too ashamed to face me these days.

639
00:39:25,204 --> 00:39:26,920
Too ashamed to face you?

640
00:39:38,720 --> 00:39:40,267
Where's Qing Ye?

641
00:39:40,267 --> 00:39:41,399
She left.

642
00:39:41,399 --> 00:39:43,520
- What about the ice cream?
- You've been working hard.

643
00:39:43,520 --> 00:39:44,892
You can have two.

644
00:39:44,892 --> 00:39:46,240
All right.

645
00:39:46,240 --> 00:39:48,862
What did you two do last night?

646
00:39:48,862 --> 00:39:50,564
None of your business.

647
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:08,440
You're here. Everything you wanted is here.

648
00:40:08,440 --> 00:40:11,025
That'll be 220 yuan in total.

649
00:40:11,680 --> 00:40:13,600
Can you make it cheaper?

650
00:40:13,600 --> 00:40:16,048
This is already the lowest price.

651
00:40:16,845 --> 00:40:18,720
This handsome guy...

652
00:40:18,720 --> 00:40:21,384
It's Xing Wu. You know him?

653
00:40:21,384 --> 00:40:22,587
He's my cousin.

654
00:40:22,587 --> 00:40:24,782
Your... your cousin?

655
00:40:25,840 --> 00:40:28,040
Okay, I'll give you 20% off.

656
00:40:28,040 --> 00:40:29,878
That's 176 yuan.

657
00:40:29,878 --> 00:40:31,280
Really?

658
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:34,080
I'm lucky to have such a cousin!

659
00:40:34,080 --> 00:40:38,001
Not exactly. He often helps me fix things.

660
00:40:38,001 --> 00:40:40,720
So it's only right to give him a discount.

661
00:40:40,720 --> 00:40:43,321
For miles around, if anything breaks at home,

662
00:40:43,321 --> 00:40:46,640
everyone asks him to fix it.
Even the cats know him.

663
00:40:46,640 --> 00:40:49,235
- The QR code is right there.
- Okay.

664
00:41:05,720 --> 00:41:07,280
<i>Thanks to my famous cousin,</i>

665
00:41:07,280 --> 00:41:09,170
<i>I got a discount on the printing.</i>

666
00:41:23,680 --> 00:41:27,022
[Xuan Island Hair Services Price List]

667
00:41:36,241 --> 00:41:38,210
Qing Ye made this?

668
00:41:40,124 --> 00:41:44,413
Wu, the neck brace you're wearing
is Qing Ye's too, right?

669
00:41:49,400 --> 00:41:50,880
Xuan Island is all set now.

670
00:41:50,880 --> 00:41:52,599
With a poster of this quality,

671
00:41:52,599 --> 00:41:54,952
I'm sure business will pick up.

672
00:41:58,990 --> 00:42:01,750
By the way, I have some more good news.

673
00:42:02,720 --> 00:42:04,910
- What is it?
- My sister's business trip is over.

674
00:42:04,910 --> 00:42:09,445
- She's coming back today.
- Really? She didn't tell me.

675
00:42:10,160 --> 00:42:12,976
She probably wanted to surprise you.

676
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:17,800
Did I say too much?

677
00:42:17,800 --> 00:42:19,907
Just pretend you don't know.

678
00:42:19,907 --> 00:42:21,515
Okay.

679
00:43:02,360 --> 00:43:05,805
Get in. I'll give you a ride.

680
00:43:05,805 --> 00:43:08,680
- Where are you going?
- Zhazhating.

681
00:43:08,680 --> 00:43:10,720
Get in. Don't worry, I'm not a bad guy.

682
00:43:10,720 --> 00:43:12,797
And I won't charge you.

683
00:43:15,476 --> 00:43:17,086
Okay.

684
00:43:22,016 --> 00:43:24,680
Too much stuff in the back.
Just sit in the front.

685
00:43:24,680 --> 00:43:27,519
- Okay, thank you.
- Here's some tissue. Dry your hair with it.

686
00:43:27,519 --> 00:43:29,610
[Hainan Specialty]

687
00:43:30,240 --> 00:43:31,867
Hainan?

688
00:43:31,867 --> 00:43:35,039
Yes. I just got back from there.
